	(text "VOUT1 -> VSYS: unused-BUCK1 official tie-off per nPM1300 PS Fig.56 (Config 2 mirror);\nVOUT pin is the buck feedback/sense node - never float. SW1 stays NC, VSET1/PVSS1 = GND (2026-07-16)."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
