	(text "FRONT-END (§4, 2026-07-14 落圖更正): USB-C flip pair = rAx+rBx (canonical: CC A5<->B5, D+ A6<->B6). §4.2 8-net 集合反插時 4 線落在 B2/B3/A10/A11 (NC) → 改 FLIP-PAIR 6-net: (A6+B6)=FSR0 (A7+B7)=FSR1 (A2+B2)=FSR2 (A3+B3)=FSR3 (A11+B11)=FSR4 (A10+B10)=SPARE。方向無關 → §4.4 掃描表作廢 (FW 固定映射 Y0..Y5)。v1 禁的鏡射對綁=A2+B11 (跨 pair, 短路 TX/RX) — 與本 pair 綁法不同。CC 方向偵測保留 (FPC 在席判定)"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 773.938 152.146 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
		)
		(uuid "7be24c42-97ae-5e72-92e5-de08f39fc5ce")
	)
	(text "PMIC_INT = nPM1300 GPIO0 push-pull (owner 2026-07-14) — no external pull-up. V3V3_FSR total decoupling ≤10µF (LOADSW 25mA soft-start)"
